Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda bertekad sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya, Shirley Grantz,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berikrar setia sepanjang hayat\Npada Yang Mulia Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa ini tidak berlebihan seperti drama?{\i0}
